{"tid":1007871,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Final Fantasy XIV 新擴張資料片於7月2日推出, 將與NieR 和 FF15合作","createTime":"2019-02-04T05:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T01:27:21.000Z","uid":43750,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c702f7092e9e6746e833b67f9b097de861264bfc","tid":1007871,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"　SQUARE ENIX 在 2 月 3 日在巴黎舉行的《Final Fantasy XIV》線下活動<br />\n「FINAL FANTASY XIV FAN FESTIVAL 2019 in Paris」的演講中，公布新擴張資料片《Final Fantasy XIV：漆黑的反叛者》的資訊，以及早期通行開始日期。<br />\n早期通行預定從 6 月 28 日開始。典藏版的預購將從 2 月 6 日開始。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyZY6b0V4AACyUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyZY6b0V4AACyUf.jpg&h=5319d934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/obkNOE-lRf0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FobkNOE-lRf0&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=7c396906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/obkNOE-lRf0</a><br />\n<br />\nPC / PS4「典藏版」發售<br />\n<br />\n　　典藏版準備了 PC 版和 PlayStation 4 版兩種。由天野喜孝繪製的美術盒裝中，收藏了「暗黑騎士」的高品質 Figure、「漆黑的反叛者」的視覺藝術畫冊和 Logo 貼紙，以及至今為止在《Final Fantasy XIV》中的插圖而印刷的「美術圖撲克」。<br />\n<br />\n　　同時，作為遊戲內道具「芙蘭」的寵物、與暗黑騎士相稱的新坐騎「グラニ」，以及作為新職業的「Gunbreaker」所使用的武器為《Final Fantasy VIII》主角史克爾使用的「リボルバ―」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dyanuc-VAAECruv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyanuc-VAAECruv.jpg&h=b709cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyanvMwU0AAw_CX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyanvMwU0AAw_CX.jpg&h=f83ed428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyZJU9WUwAE97Hv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyZJU9WUwAE97Hv.jpg&h=470cc681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyanvrNUUAA2UoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyanvrNUUAA2UoM.jpg&h=c3f08d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyanwJ3VAAABh-L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyanwJ3VAAABh-L.jpg&h=14ee874d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/300e6a4b8b39d340ef71598202b524df.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F300e6a4b8b39d340ef71598202b524df.JPG&h=ac157abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預購特典的提早通行是從 6 月 28 日開始<br />\n<br />\n　　預購特典包含從 6 月 28 日開始的提早通行資格、寵物「グレムリン」，以及狀態會根據等級而變化的飾品「以太之光耳環」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/de966d8b60a8daf6dad42a772ea3171f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2Fde966d8b60a8daf6dad42a772ea3171f.JPG&h=08341ddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"334c14a034a2a2d61ed0d066afb747089807f844","tid":1007871,"uid":43750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5.0資料片情報</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新職業</span></strong> <strong>GUNBREAKER</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyZR6ZsVsAEhc9z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyZR6ZsVsAEhc9z.jpg&h=02bacd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/f54ad3dad4d78ce1532a804aae12cca5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2Ff54ad3dad4d78ce1532a804aae12cca5.JPG&h=13e27d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/39534a7546753795f06edfbbea715c72.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A