umbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F4df9f073e89510673fe89c925734f816.JPG&h=4d9777d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/eb15a0d30f58dd7d493ebf531cd7d0a6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2Feb15a0d30f58dd7d493ebf531cd7d0a6.JPG&h=10f814b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新蠻族</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/01ed469b5d08be4b5a6890bf12c847af.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F01ed469b5d08be4b5a6890bf12c847af.JPG&h=39e6b83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/ada59568b120b907db766db9f03f79c8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2Fada59568b120b907db766db9f03f79c8.JPG&h=4399c719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新蠻神</span></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/8a322e372da35c9b98169d0e12333a6b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F8a322e372da35c9b98169d0e12333a6b.JPG&h=bd54e7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/7b641c3c031c79de94bff295c28c8df8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F7b641c3c031c79de94bff295c28c8df8.JPG&h=f469b0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新種族 - Viera</span></strong> / <strong>ヴィエラ</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/6336a29905038209d65c84542a3dda61.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F6336a29905038209d65c84542a3dda61.JPG&h=0fcdfd2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是最後一次在《Final Fantasy XIV》中追加種族<br />\n<br />\n　　「ヴィエラ」是《Final Fantasy XII》中擁有兔耳的種族<br />\n在「紅蓮的解放者」的團隊任務「重返伊瓦利斯」中<br />\n《Final Fantasy XII》的芙蘭（フラン）作為客串人物登場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/6b0fe762245915c03488660f2d446086.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F6b0fe762245915c03488660f2d446086.JPG&h=9d6c00dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/f1b3b34fa2a80a0e326551a2702f049d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2Ff1b3b34fa2a80a0e326551a2702f049d.JPG&h=daaaa053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N8JE4-T-i0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN8JE4-T-i0s&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=75db6f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N8JE4-T-i0s</a>"},{"pid":"aef55d5d874f37d819ad4ebf32afd46ffa7d711b","tid":1007871,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合作內容</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">NieR:Automata</span></strong><br />\n新24人副本 - Dark Apocalypse<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/08bdc455b8e0a4908c3679a878a12d8f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F08bdc455b8e0a4908c3679a878a12d8f.JPG&h=8463d68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/umadori0726/imgs/1/6/16d5bdf4-s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fumadori0726%2Fimgs%2F1%2F6%2F16d5bdf4-s.jpg&h=3a398e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/umadori0726/imgs/7/5/7514db91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fumadori0726%2Fimgs%